paper_abstract: The quasi-gasdynamic equation system and the numerical algorithm for non-stationary viscous gasdynamic flow calculations are presented. The quasi-gasdynamic equation system generalizes the Navier-Stokes equations and differs from it by the additional dissipative terms. The numerical examples are presented. paper_title: Quasi-gasdynamic numerical algorithm for gas flow simulations
